PrecisHIV-INFECTED PERSONS AND THALIDOMIDE VICTIMS ASSOCIATION ORDER - which provides for the making of ex gratia payments to individuals who received HIV-infected blood or blood products and to individuals whose mothers were administered "Kevadon" or "Talimol" (thalidomide) and consequently suffered physical deformities.
